h1 | Getting There

#airports
	The closest commonly used local airports are San Francisco International Airport and Oakland International Airport.
	It will take about an hour and a half to drive from SFO to Petaluma, and about an hour to drive up from OAK, traffic permitting.
	One other option is the Sonoma County Airport (STS), which is located in Santa Rosa.
	Alaska Airlines offers flights into STS.  It will take about ten minutes to drive from STS to Petaluma.

